		<title>Why Some Freelance Writers Earn Big Bucks While Most Slave for Peanuts</title>
		<link>http://www.makealivingwriting.com/why-freelance-writers-earn-big-bucks/</link>
		<comments>http://www.makealivingwriting.com/why-freelance-writers-earn-big-bucks/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 30 Nov 2014 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
