		<description><![CDATA[<p>Have you wondered if there&#8217;s a point at which the freelance writing life gets easier? I get asked that a lot. Writers get sick of the hustle and grind of trying to scare up more gigs. Or they tire of<span class="ellipsis">&#8230;</span>
