<p>With a deep breath, I pressed "send" on an email containing months of research and my first article for a <a title="Caroltice.com - 5 good paying writing niches" href="http://www.caroltice.com/5-good-paying-writing-niches" target="_blank">trade magazine</a>.</p>
<p>It was done!</p>
